'''拉德西卡·阿普泰'''（राधिका आपटे，{{bd|1985年|9月7日}}）是[[印度|印度]]裔的電影及舞台劇女演員<ref>{{cite news|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/news-interviews/Radhika-Apte-Anurag-Kashyap-bonding-well/articleshow/25990330.cms?|title=Radhika Apte- Anurag Kashyap bonding well|work=The Times of India|date=19 November 2013|accessdate=6 January 2014|archive-date=2013-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131119201226/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/entertainment/bollywood/news-interviews/Radhika-Apte-Anurag-Kashyap-bonding-well/articleshow/25990330.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿普泰在印度[[马哈拉施特拉邦|马哈拉施特拉邦]]的[[浦那|浦那]]長大，一開始是在她家鄉的Aasakta劇團中演出。阿普泰首次電影演出是在2005年[[宝莱坞|宝莱坞]]的奇幻電影《{{le|哇！这就是生活|Vaah! Life Ho Toh Aisi!}}》。

阿普泰第一次擔任主要角色的電影是2009年[[孟加拉语|孟加拉语]]的社會電影《{{le|无尽的等待|Antaheen}}》（Antaheen），第一部[[馬拉地語|馬拉地語]]的電影是2009年的浪漫悲劇《{{le|Samaantar|Samaantar}}》<ref name="imdb">{{cite web|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1560171/|title=Samaantar (2009) - IMDb|publisher=imdb.com|accessdate=1 November 2015|archive-date=2017-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170210061049/http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1560171/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿普泰在2015年開始在宝莱坞走紅，拍攝了驚悚電影《{{le|复仇之城|Badlapur (film)}}》（Badlapur）及喜劇《{{le|Hunterrr|Hunterrr}}》、《{{le|印度愚公|Manjhi - The Mountain Man}}》（Manjhi - The Mountain Man），在2016年拍攝心理驚悚電影《{{le|Phobia|Phobia (2016 film)}}》，受到普遍的讚賞<ref name="newindianexpress">{{cite web|url=http://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/hindi/I-Wondered-if-Nawaz-Didnt-Like-Me/2015/07/16/article2923048.ece|title='I Wondered if Nawaz Didn't Like Me' - The New Indian Express|publisher=newindianexpress.com|accessdate=1 November 2015|archive-date=2015-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151031202955/http://www.newindianexpress.com/entertainment/hindi/I-Wondered-if-Nawaz-Didnt-Like-Me/2015/07/16/article2923048.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="india.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.india.com/showbiz/radhika-apte-is-the-new-age-ahalya-the-next-big-star-of-bollywood-473673/|title=Radhika Apte: Is the new age Ahalya the next big star of Bollywood? | Latest News & Gossip on Popular Trends at India.com|publisher=india.com|accessdate=1 November 2015|archive-date=2015-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151008163121/http://www.india.com/showbiz/radhika-apte-is-the-new-age-ahalya-the-next-big-star-of-bollywood-473673/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="hindustantimes.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/brunch-stories/she-s-doing-films-in-six-languages-who-is-radhika-apte-anyway/article1-1333825.aspx|title=She’s doing films in six languages! Who is Radhika Apte, anyway? | brunch | Hindustan Times|publisher=hindustantimes.com|accessdate=1 November 2015|archive-date=2015-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150825040506/http://www.hindustantimes.com/brunch-stories/she-s-doing-films-in-six-languages-who-is-radhika-apte-anyway/article1-1333825.aspx|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。後來又在二部電影中擔任主要角色，2014年馬拉地語的驚悚電影《{{le|为愛而戰 (2014年電影)|Lai Bhaari|为愛而戰}}》（Lai Bhaari）及2016年泰米爾語的黑幫電影《[[卡巴里|卡巴里]]》（Kabali）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160721004158-260408 |title=印度企業放一天假 讓員工看電影 |access-date=2017-02-20 |archive-date=2017-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170221011250/http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160721004158-260408 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

